snippet: The latest report brings the total number of Tibetans who have taken their lives to protest Chinese rule since March 2009 to 20.
abstract: Reports have surfaced of another self-immolation in Tibet, bringing to at least 20 the number of Tibetans who have taken their lives to protest Chinese rule since March 2009.
lead_paragraph: The latest report brings the total number of Tibetans who have taken their lives to protest Chinese rule since March 2009 to 20.

headline.main: China: Exile Groups Report Another Self-Immolation in Tibet
